    <p>South Korean boy band Got7 (above) re­turn with a full stu­dio al­bum, which in­clude Breath and Last Piece. Breath is the more melo­di­ous and sweeter of the two and the whistling in the cho­rus makes for a nice touch, while Last Piece is a more tra­di­tional high-en­ergy K-pop dance track.</p>
    <p>Much of the al­bum’s lyrics and mu­sic were writ­ten by the mem­bers them­selves.</p>

